---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import { breadcrumbLd } from '../../utils/jsonld';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const crumbLd = breadcrumbLd([
  { name: '首頁', item: 'https://noblerise.com.tw/' },
  { name: '最新消息', item: 'https://noblerise.com.tw/news/' },
]);
---
<BaseLayout
  title="最新消息 | 諾昇理財規劃"
  description="諾昇理財規劃最新消息：全方位財務規劃 × 115年所得稅申報實務講座，由 CFP® 張惠芳主講，帶您科學化盤點財務全貌、合法節稅不踩雷。"
>
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify(crumbLd)} />

  <PageHero
    eyebrow="獨立理財規劃講座"
    title="全方位財務規劃<br>× 115年所得稅申報實務"
    description="一場讓您從「理財焦慮」走向「財務幸福」的關鍵講座"
    backgroundImage="images/aboutmehead.jpg"
  />

  <main class="news-body">

    <!-- 財務困惑 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>您的財務，是否也有這些困惑？</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-pain-grid">
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>財富增長</h4>
          <p>薪水月月入帳，卻不知道錢去了哪裡？努力工作十年，財富累積的速度，是否讓您感到失望？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>退休規劃</h4>
          <p>距離退休還有多少年？您心中有一個具體的數字嗎？還是只能靠「感覺」，覺得應該夠了？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>保險保障</h4>
          <p>保單買了，心裡卻還是不踏實，「這樣夠嗎？」「有沒有買重複？」「保費是不是浪費了？」這些問題，您有答案嗎？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>稅務規劃</h4>
          <p>所得稅三大新制上路，租金扣除額改制、幼兒學前取消排富、海外投資申報規定，每一條都影響您的實際稅負。您確定自己了解了嗎？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>投資策略</h4>
          <p>您的投資，是根據自己的財務目標規劃的，還是跟著市場情緒走？賺了一段，卻又在下跌時全吐回去？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pain-card">
          <h4>買房換屋</h4>
          <p>買房，是您一生最大的財務決策之一。但您是否真的算過，以您目前的財務狀況，現在買對嗎？</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 講座重點主題 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>3小時財務課程，您將獲得的 5 大財務升級</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-topic-list">
        <div class="news-topic-item">
          <div class="news-topic-num">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4>金錢自動配置</h4>
            <p>如何有效運用錢，把錢花在刀口上，讓錢自動化管理。建立屬於您的「薪資分配系統」，讓每一分錢都發揮最大效益。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-topic-item">
          <div class="news-topic-num">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4>財務健康指數</h4>
            <p>買房還是租房？貸款投資前，您必須先知道的事。用科學指數評估自己的財務體質，做出最符合人生目標的決定。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-topic-item">
          <div class="news-topic-num">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4>保險量化防護</h4>
            <p>全面檢視現有保單，以最少預算達到最適保障，讓每一分保費都花在刀口上。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-topic-item">
          <div class="news-topic-num">4</div>
          <div>
            <h4>長線投資策略</h4>
            <p>0050 / S&amp;P 500 vs 全方位規劃，退休金到底差多少？不盲從市場情緒，用系統化配置讓資產長期穩健增長。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-topic-item">
          <div class="news-topic-num">5</div>
          <div>
            <h4>所得稅務申報</h4>
            <p>115年報稅實戰，海外投資所得稅申報，合法節稅不踩雷。掌握申報眉角，讓辛苦賺來的錢留在自己口袋。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 這堂課適合誰 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>這堂課適合誰？</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-audience-list">
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>高收入雙薪家庭</strong>
          <span>收入不低，卻感覺錢不夠用，想建立系統化的財務規劃</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>持有海外ETF、美股的投資人</strong>
          <span>不確定海外所得怎麼申報，擔心踩雷被補稅</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>正在考慮買房換屋</strong>
          <span>想用數字評估現在的財務體質，而不是靠感覺決定</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>剛出社會的高薪族</strong>
          <span>薪水不錯但沒有方向，想建立正確的投資與理財觀念</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>距離退休還有10-20年</strong>
          <span>想認真試算退休缺口，提前做好準備</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-audience-item">
          <strong>曾被推銷、對金融機構失去信任</strong>
          <span>想要獨立、中立的第三方財務評估與建議</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 客戶見證 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>規劃後，客戶的真實回饋</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-testi-list">

        <div class="news-testi-card">
          <div class="news-testi-card-top"></div>
          <div class="news-testi-card-inner">
            <div class="news-testi-tags">
              <span class="news-ttag-main">三明治家庭</span>
              <span class="news-ttag-sub">陪伴傳承</span>
              <span class="news-ttag-sub">父母健康・家庭財務</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="news-testi-card-title">「在最難的那一年，她不只幫我整理財務，更幫我整理人生」</h3>
            <div class="news-testi-card-sub">上有年邁父母・下有子女・財務與傳承同步規劃</div>
            <div class="news-testi-quote">
              <p>「財務整理更用說了，更是幫了我們（和我媽）的大忙」</p>
              <p>「這一路我們也算是從戰友變朋友，真的感謝神，也感激有妳♡」</p>
            </div>
            <div class="news-testi-img-wrap">
              <img src={`${base}images/testimonial-letter.jpg`} alt="客戶手寫親筆信" class="news-testi-img" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="news-testi-img-hint">📝 手寫親筆信</div>
            <div class="news-testi-ba">
              <div class="news-ba-box news-ba-before">
                <div class="news-ba-label">規劃前的困境</div>
                <div class="news-ba-text">同時面對媽媽的事・爸爸健康報告・家庭財務多頭馬車</div>
              </div>
              <div class="news-ba-box news-ba-after">
                <div class="news-ba-label">規劃後的改變</div>
                <div class="news-ba-text">財務有人陪伴整理・人生最難的時刻不再孤單面對</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="news-testi-card">
          <div class="news-testi-card-top"></div>
          <div class="news-testi-card-inner">
            <div class="news-testi-tags">
              <span class="news-ttag-main">認真主管</span>
              <span class="news-ttag-sub">多才多藝・企圖心強</span>
              <span class="news-ttag-sub">高收入・財務待整理</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="news-testi-card-title">「規劃後，我開始用數字做決定，不再靠感覺」</h3>
            <div class="news-testi-card-sub">收入不差但支出難管控・從財務混亂到目標清晰・立即行動</div>
            <div class="news-testi-quote">
              <p>「惠芳心思縝密、邏輯好，可以協助我去思考我不曾想過的問題」</p>
              <p>「用錢更謹慎，對未來的想法更確立」</p>
            </div>
            <div class="news-testi-img-wrap">
              <img src={`${base}images/testimonial-survey2.jpg`} alt="客戶規劃回饋問卷" class="news-testi-img" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="news-testi-img-hint">📋 真實規劃回饋問卷</div>
            <div class="news-testi-ba">
              <div class="news-ba-box news-ba-before">
                <div class="news-ba-label">規劃前的困境</div>
                <div class="news-ba-text">沒有財務目標・支出較難管控・想買房但不知道時機</div>
              </div>
              <div class="news-ba-box news-ba-after">
                <div class="news-ba-label">規劃後的改變</div>
                <div class="news-ba-text">開始執行記帳節流・規劃買房換車目標・對未來更確立</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 主講人介紹 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>主講人介紹</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-speaker-card">
        <div class="news-speaker-inner">
          <div class="news-speaker-photo-col">
            <img src={`${base}images/yvonne-cfp.jpeg`} alt="首席顧問 張惠芳 CFP®" class="news-speaker-photo" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="news-speaker-info">
            <div class="news-spk-name">張惠芳</div>
            <div class="news-spk-sub">諾昇理財首席規劃顧問</div>
            <div class="news-spk-stats">
              <div><div class="news-stat-val">20+</div><div class="news-stat-lbl">年金融實戰經驗</div></div>
              <div><div class="news-stat-val">IFA</div><div class="news-stat-lbl">獨立理財規劃顧問</div></div>
              <div>
                <div class="news-stat-val"><img src={`${base}images/cfp-logo.png`} alt="CFP®" class="news-cfp-logo" /></div>
                <div class="news-stat-lbl">國際認證高級理財規劃顧問</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="news-stat-val"><img src={`${base}images/rfa-logo.png`} alt="RFA" class="news-cfp-logo" /></div>
                <div class="news-stat-lbl">退休理財規劃顧問</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="news-stat-val"><img src={`${base}images/fchfp-logo.jpg`} alt="FChFP" class="news-cfp-logo" /></div>
                <div class="news-stat-lbl">特許財務規劃師</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="news-stat-val">信託</div>
                <div class="news-stat-lbl">家族信託規劃顧問師</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="news-spk-bio">惠芳以「財務幸福」為核心理念，不受任何金融機構 KPI 影響，以獨立理財規劃顧問（IFA）立場，提供中立、專業、以客戶利益優先的財務建議。曾榮獲 FPAT 2022 理財規劃書競賽最佳顧問獎，多次受邀媒體採訪分享財務規劃觀點。</p>
            <div>
              <div class="news-media-label">媒體專欄與專訪</div>
              <div class="news-media-tags">
                <span class="news-mtag news-mtag--gold">TVBS 專訪</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">風傳媒</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">天下雜誌</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">今周刊</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">Smart</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">橘世代</span>
                <span class="news-mtag">商周財富網</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href={`${base}about/`} class="news-spk-more">了解更多</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 活動資訊 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>活動資訊</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-event-card">
        <div class="news-ec-header">
          <div class="news-ec-header-icon">📋</div>
          <div>
            <h3>講座基本資訊</h3>
            <p>115年4月25日（六）　報到 13:10 ／ 講座 13:30　淡江大學城區部 D209 教室</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-ec-grid">
          <div class="news-ec-item">
            <div class="news-ec-icon">📅</div>
            <div>
              <span class="news-ec-label">日期與時間</span>
              <span class="news-ec-val">115年4月25日（六）</span>
              <span class="news-ec-sub">報到：13:10 開始<br>講座：13:30 – 16:30</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="news-ec-item">
            <div class="news-ec-icon">📍</div>
            <div>
              <span class="news-ec-label">活動地點</span>
              <span class="news-ec-val">淡江大學城區部 D209 教室</span>
              <span class="news-ec-sub">台北市大安區金華街199巷5號<br>東門捷運站（淡水信義線／中和新蘆線）</span>
              <a class="news-map-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=台北市大安區金華街199巷5號" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                在 Google Maps 查看地圖 →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="news-ec-item">
            <div class="news-ec-icon">🎤</div>
            <div>
              <span class="news-ec-label">主講人</span>
              <span class="news-ec-val">張惠芳 CFP®</span>
              <span class="news-ec-sub">諾昇理財首席規劃顧問｜20年金融實戰經驗</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="news-ec-item">
            <div class="news-ec-icon">🎁</div>
            <div>
              <span class="news-ec-label">出席好禮</span>
              <span class="news-ec-val">出席即送雙重禮</span>
              <span class="news-ec-sub">① 1對1財務諮詢（市值 NT$5,000）<br>② 115年所得稅懶人包（所得稅心智圖）</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 報名費用 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>報名費用</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-pricing-card">
        <div class="news-pricing-header">
          <div class="news-pricing-header-icon">💳</div>
          <div>
            <h3>講座費用</h3>
            <p>早鳥優惠 4/10 前每人 NT$900，多人同行更優惠</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pricing-grid">
          <div class="news-price-item news-price-item--promo">
            <span class="news-promo-badge">早鳥價 4/10 前</span>
            <span class="news-price-amount">900<small> 元</small></span>
            <span class="news-price-tag">每人 NT$900</span>
          </div>
          <div class="news-price-item">
            <span class="news-price-label">單人</span>
            <span class="news-price-amount">1,000<small> 元</small></span>
            <span class="news-price-tag">NT$1,000 / 人</span>
          </div>
          <div class="news-price-item">
            <span class="news-price-label">兩人同行</span>
            <span class="news-price-amount">1,800<small> 元</small></span>
            <span class="news-price-tag">NT$900 / 人</span>
          </div>
          <div class="news-price-item news-price-item--promo">
            <span class="news-promo-badge">優惠碼</span>
            <span class="news-price-amount">800<small> 元</small></span>
            <span class="news-price-tag">每人 NT$800</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-pricing-note">早鳥價：4/10 前報名每人 NT$900，現省 NT$100｜持優惠碼報名每人 NT$800</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- 出席即送好禮 -->
    <div class="news-section-head"><h2>出席即送好禮</h2></div>
    <div class="news-block">
      <div class="news-gifts-grid">
        <div class="news-gift-card">
          <div class="news-gift-num">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4>1對1 財務諮詢（1小時）</h4>
            <div class="news-gift-value">市值 NT$5,000</div>
            <div class="news-gift-note">限出席本人於講座後 <strong>2個月內</strong> 預約，僅限 <strong>平日白天</strong> 時段，請提前安排。</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-gift-card">
          <div class="news-gift-num">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4>115年所得稅懶人包</h4>
            <div class="news-gift-value">所得稅心智圖</div>
            <div class="news-gift-note">由 CFP® 專業整理，一張圖看懂所得稅重點，A3彩色輸出贈送。</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-divider"></div>

    <!-- CTA 報名 -->
    <div class="news-cta">
      <div class="news-cta-eyebrow">名額有限 · 報名截止 4/12</div>
      <h2 class="news-cta-title">財務幸福，從這一步開始<br><em>4/25 等您一起走這條路</em></h2>
      <p class="news-cta-sub">名額有限，額滿截止，報名截止日 115/4/12，立刻確認您的座位</p>
      <a href="https://forms.gle/b7v1gvohc4ri8LBK6" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="news-cta-btn">立即購票</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Layout ── */
  .news-body {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 28px 80px;
  }
  .news-block { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .news-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-border), transparent);
    margin: 56px 0;
  }

  /* ── Section Head ── */
  .news-section-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .news-section-head::before {
    content: '';
    width: 4px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .news-section-head h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    font-weight: var(--heading-weight);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── Audience ── */
  .news-audience-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .news-audience-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    background: var(--color-white);
